<subSubSection pageId="70" pageNumber="71" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="70.[151,1436,973,1358]" pageId="70" pageNumber="71">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,315,1261,1286]" pageId="70" pageNumber="71">Remarks.</emphasis>
The species is fairly similar to 
<emphasis box="[709,888,1261,1286]" italics="true" pageId="70" pageNumber="71">Planapheretima</emphasis>
<taxonomicName authority="Chen, 1946" authorityName="Chen" authorityYear="1946" box="[902,1173,1261,1286]" class="Clitellata" family="Megascolecidae" genus="Pheretima" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Haplotaxida" pageId="70" pageNumber="71" phylum="Annelida" rank="species" species="lacertina">
<emphasis box="[902,1003,1261,1286]" italics="true" pageId="70" pageNumber="71">lacertina</emphasis>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Chen" box="[1024,1165,1261,1286]" pageId="70" pageNumber="71" refString="Chen, Y. (1946) On the terrestrial oligochaeta from Szechuan III. Contributions from the Biological Laboratory of the Science Society of China, Zoological Series, 16, 83 - 141." type="journal article" year="1946">Chen, 1946</bibRefCitation>
)
</taxonomicName>
, but differs in having spermathecal pores paired in 5/6/7 dorsally and pigments dorsally (
<bibRefCitation author="Thai" box="[950,1075,1297,1322]" pageId="70" pageNumber="71" refString="Thai, T. B. (1997) New data on leaf - crawlers Pheretima Kinberg, 1863 in Vietnam and a key to species of this group from the mainland of Asia. TAP CHI SINH HOC, 19 (3), 1 - 7." type="journal article" year="1997">Thai 1997</bibRefCitation>
). 
<bibRefCitation author="Thai" box="[1099,1237,1297,1322]" pageId="70" pageNumber="71" refString="Thai, T. B. (1983) Earthworms of Vietnam (Systematic, fauna, distribution and zoogeographic). PhD dissertation in Zooglogy. Lomonosov Moscow State University, Russia [in Russian]" type="book" year="1983">Thai (1983)</bibRefCitation>
proposed a new subgenus 
<emphasis box="[262,345,1334,1357]" italics="true" pageId="70" pageNumber="71">Terrata</emphasis>
of the genus 
<taxonomicName box="[496,612,1333,1358]" class="Clitellata" family="Megascolecidae" genus="Pheretima" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Haplotaxida" pageId="70" pageNumber="71" phylum="Annelida" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[496,612,1333,1358]" italics="true" pageId="70" pageNumber="71">Pheretima</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, and placed the species under the new subgenus.
</paragraph>
